n|Morocco}} [[Morocco]] (*1997)\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 4.5*\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"|\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 27,000*\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 400,000*\n|-\n|{{flagicon|South Africa}} [[South Africa]] (*2008)\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| \u22482.5*<ref name=\"cssr\">{{cite web | url=http://www.cssr.uct.ac.za/sites/cssr.uct.ac.za/files/pubs/WP221.pdf | title=SURVEY OF BEEKEEPING IN SOUTH AFRICA | publisher=Centre for Social Science Research | date=July 2008 | accessdate=January 23, 2012 | author1=Conradie, Beatrice | author2=Nortj\u00e9, Bronwyn | lastauthoramp=yes | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121202035254/http://www.cssr.uct.ac.za/sites/cssr.uct.ac.za/files/pubs/WP221.pdf | archive-date=December 2, 2012 | url-status=dead | df=mdy-all }}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| \u22481.5*<ref name=\"cssr\" />\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| \u22481,790*<ref name=\"cssr\" />\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| \u224892,000*<ref name=\"cssr\" />\n|-\n| colspan=\"5\"|<small>''Source: Food and Agriculture Organization of the United Nations<ref>{{cite web |url=http://faostat.fao.org/site/340/default.aspx |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070310232049/http://faostat.fao.org/site/340/default.aspx |archivedate=2007-03-10 |title=FAOSTAT}}</ref><br/>\n</small>\n|}\n<small>Sources:\n*Denmark: beekeeping.com<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.beekeeping.com/countries/denmark.htm|title=Apiservices \u2013 Beekeeping \u2013 Apiculture \u2013 Denmark/Danemark|website=Beekeeping.com|accessdate=2016-03-12}}</ref> (1996)\n*Arab countries: beekeeping.com<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.beekeeping.com/articles/us/arab_countries.htm|title=The Future of Bees and Honey Production in Arab Countries|website=Beekeeping.com|accessdate=2016-03-12}}</ref> (1997)\n*US: University of Arkansas National Agricultural Law Center,<ref>{{cite web|title=Farm Commodity Programs: Honey|url=http://www.nationalaglawcenter.org/wp-content/uploads/assets/crs/RS20759.pdf|